

Build and run CPU version:
	docker compose up --build


Build and run GPU version (NVIDIA GPU required):
	docker compose up --build --detach --gpus all


Check GPU usage inside the container:
	docker exec -it synonym-generator nvidia-smi


After completion, synonyms.txt will appear in your project folder with the formatted synonym mappings.


This setup is ready-to-run — you just need to drop your .txt files into texts/.


